name: LifeQuotes
0:
”Alexa, open Life Quotes”
”Alexa, start Life Quotes”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: life quotes
des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of life learning quotes. Quotes that would help you to see light at the end of the tunnel, and give you that extra burst of hope and courage to persevere and succeed in this journey called "life." 
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
